description:
Did you know that there is a version of Google Chrome that is actually an operating system? Well, in this video we're taking a look at such an operating system! Chrome OS Flex is a special version of Chrome OS, which works in computers that were not specifically built for this OS. This operating system works similar to Firefox OS, but instead of being made for phones, it's for laptops.

Next video: MX Linux
